title: Eat Pizza
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Pizzeria with several locations (Glenroy, Maribyrnong). Sometimes has in-stock Cheezly vegan cheese, vegan ham and salami for an extra charge each topping, but do call and check ahead. Mostly take-out with some seating. Has gluten-free.
